20609b0 : filesystem: Replace Surge::filesystem with ghc::filesystem
Thu, 21 Jan 2021 11:13:57 +0100
Matthias von Faber

filesystem: Replace Surge::filesystem with ghc::filesystem

This replaces the implementation with gulrak's filesystem
(https://github.com/gulrak/filesystem) on systems without a usable
std::filesystem, or on any system (including Windows), when the
SURGE_FILESYSTEM_FORCE_GHC CMake cache variable is set.
